            "text": "{\"sitones\":[{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509fad30aea74ec34b81b\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_2019_blackbox\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_2019_blackbox\",\"name\":\"2019 黑箱小石\",\"type\":\"exploration\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"小石撿到一個神祕箱子，裡面裝著看似會自己決定一切的演算法。牠決定先不要害怕，而是把箱子慢慢打開。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_2019_blackbox.png\",\"abilityName\":\"拾荒直覺\",\"abilityKind\":\"material_drop_rate\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰結束時小石掉落率提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a450a05d30aea74ec34b829\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_2020_tour_flag\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_2020_tour_flag\",\"name\":\"2020 導遊旗小石\",\"type\":\"resonance\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠舉起小旗子，帶第一次參加 SITCON 的人認識年會攤位和工作人員。總會讓人想開口問問題。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_2020_tour_flag.png\",\"abilityName\":\"亮晶晶\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509ffd30aea74ec34b821\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_2021_abacus\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_2021_abacus\",\"name\":\"2021 算盤小石\",\"type\":\"inspiration\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把一顆顆算珠推來推去，像是在摸索計算機最早的影子。每一次撥動，都是現代技術往前疊起來的一小步。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_2021_abacus.png\",\"abilityName\":\"靈光一閃\",\"abilityKind\":\"eliminate_wrong_choice\",\"abilityValue\":15,\"abilityCount\":1,\"abilityDescription\":\"題目開始時有 15% 機率刪去 1 個錯誤選項。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509fcd30aea74ec34b81d\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_2022_maze\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_2022_maze\",\"name\":\"2022 迷宮小石\",\"type\":\"exploration\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"人生的技能樹選擇，就像迷宮裡的不同叉路。迷宮小石有時像 DFS 一樣，選定一條路就深入嘗試；有時也像 BFS 一樣，先廣泛探索各種可能。每個人的走法都不一樣，但只要持續探索，就能慢慢找出自己的出口。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_2022_maze.png\",\"abilityName\":\"拾荒直覺\",\"abilityKind\":\"material_drop_rate\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰結束時小石掉落率提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a450a00d30aea74ec34b823\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_2024_finite\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_2024_finite\",\"name\":\"2024 有限小石\",\"type\":\"inspiration\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠知道時間、體力和注意力都有限，所以開始學會選擇真正重要的問題。限制沒有讓牠停下來，反而讓牠的思考更清楚。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_2024_finite.png\",\"abilityName\":\"靈光一閃\",\"abilityKind\":\"eliminate_wrong_choice\",\"abilityValue\":15,\"abilityCount\":1,\"abilityDescription\":\"題目開始時有 15% 機率刪去 1 個錯誤選項。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509f4d30aea74ec34b813\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_2024_ribbon\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_2024_ribbon\",\"name\":\"2024 彩帶小石\",\"type\":\"entertainment\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把活動現場的笑聲、掌聲和混亂都捲進彩帶裡。每次彩帶散開，基地就多一點營隊的聲音。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_2024_ribbon.png\",\"abilityName\":\"掌聲加成\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509fdd30aea74ec34b81f\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_booth\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_booth\",\"name\":\"攤位小石\",\"type\":\"exploration\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"身上貼滿各個社群攤位的貼紙，每張都代表一次開口問問題的勇氣。貼紙越多，牠越像一本會走路的社群地圖。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_booth.png\",\"abilityName\":\"拾荒直覺\",\"abilityKind\":\"material_drop_rate\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰結束時小石掉落率提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a45043ed30aea74ec34b7c1\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_camp_backpack\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_camp_backpack\",\"name\":\"營地背包小石\",\"type\":\"exploration\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把貼紙、名牌、備用線材都塞進包包，準備在 2026 營隊裡探索下一個任務。但是包包有點重\\u003e_\\u003c\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_camp_backpack.png\",\"abilityName\":\"拾荒直覺\",\"abilityKind\":\"material_drop_rate\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰結束時小石掉落率提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4e141a814f1866e81b7336\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_command_blind_trip\",\"quantity\":2,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_command_blind_trip\",\"name\":\"指令盲旅小石\",\"type\":\"engineering\",\"rarity\":\"limited\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠戴上眼罩後等待隊友把混亂變成一套清楚的指令。每一次成功抵達，都是大家共同定義出來的路。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_command_blind_trip.png\",\"abilityName\":\"指令校準\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":15,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 15%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a450a07d30aea74ec34b82b\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_community_handshake\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_community_handshake\",\"name\":\"社群握手小石\",\"type\":\"resonance\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠第一次伸手時有點緊張，但對方也剛好想認識新朋友。兩隻手碰在一起，小隊基地就多了一段可以回看的連結。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_community_handshake.png\",\"abilityName\":\"亮晶晶\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a451567d30aea74ec34b833\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_consensus_draft\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_consensus_draft\",\"name\":\"共識草稿小石\",\"type\":\"resonance\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把大家七嘴八舌的意見整理成一份還能修改的草稿。每個人都留下一點痕跡，規則才不只是某個人的決定。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_consensus_draft.png\",\"abilityName\":\"亮晶晶\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a450a08d30aea74ec34b82d\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_contribution\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_contribution\",\"name\":\"貢獻小石\",\"type\":\"resonance\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠第一次送出貢獻時，只改了一個小地方。可是有人說謝謝之後，牠發現開源不是距離很遠的大事。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_contribution.png\",\"abilityName\":\"亮晶晶\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509ebd30aea74ec34b80b\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_docker\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_docker\",\"name\":\"Docker 小石\",\"type\":\"engineering\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把環境裝進小小的容器裡，終於不用再說「我這邊可以跑」。每次啟動成功，牠都會安心地點一下頭。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_docker.png\",\"abilityName\":\"穩定輸出\",\"abilityKind\":\"answer_score_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":18,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"答對時分數提高 18%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a426647858607ca960dae9d\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_engineering_base\",\"quantity\":15,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_engineering_base\",\"name\":\"工程型小石\",\"type\":\"engineering\",\"rarity\":\"base\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠體內藏著潛力無窮的工程能量，還沒有固定成任何工具或系統。只要遇到問題，牠就會安靜觀察，準備把混亂拆成可以一步一步解開的形狀。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/basic_blue.png\",\"abilityName\":\"穩定輸出\",\"abilityKind\":\"answer_score_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":15,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"答對時分數提高 15%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a426647858607ca960dae9e\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_entertainment_base\",\"quantity\":15,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_entertainment_base\",\"name\":\"娛樂型小石\",\"type\":\"entertainment\",\"rarity\":\"base\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠帶著潛力無窮的舞台感，還不知道自己會成為表演者、主持人，還是點亮氣氛的人。只要有人願意參與，牠就會把笑聲、勇氣和回憶收進身上。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/basic_orange.png\",\"abilityName\":\"掌聲加成\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":5,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 5%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509f5d30aea74ec34b815\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_espresso\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_espresso\",\"name\":\"Espresso 小石\",\"type\":\"entertainment\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把想講的內容濃縮成一小杯，苦一點但很醒腦。短短十分鐘，也能讓人帶走一個新問題。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_espresso.png\",\"abilityName\":\"掌聲加成\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a426647858607ca960dae9a\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_explorer_base\",\"quantity\":14,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_explorer_base\",\"name\":\"探索型小石\",\"type\":\"exploration\",\"rarity\":\"base\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠是最普通、也最有可能性的小石，身上還沒有長出明確的方向。每一次逛攤位、問問題或認識新朋友，都可能讓牠展開一條潛力無窮的路。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/basic_gray.png\",\"abilityName\":\"拾荒直覺\",\"abilityKind\":\"material_drop_rate\",\"abilityValue\":5,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰結束時小石掉落率提高 5%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4e582543c646f444c0501c\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_fireside\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_fireside\",\"name\":\"爐邊小石\",\"type\":\"resonance\",\"rarity\":\"limited\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠總是在夜談時靠近火光，安靜聽完每個人的故事。有人願意開口時，牠身上的光就會亮一點。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_fireside.png\",\"abilityName\":\"夜談餘火\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":120,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 120%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509f1d30aea74ec34b80f\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_gpg\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_gpg\",\"name\":\"GPG 小石\",\"type\":\"engineering\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把訊息封進信封前，先確認鑰匙是不是交到對的人手上。安全不是神祕咒語，而是一連串可以被驗證的動作。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_gpg.png\",\"abilityName\":\"穩定輸出\",\"abilityKind\":\"answer_score_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":18,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"答對時分數提高 18%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4e1ce8814f1866e81b74c2\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_human_llm\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_human_llm\",\"name\":\"人類大語言模型小石\",\"type\":\"inspiration\",\"rarity\":\"limited\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"小石在資料矩陣裡逐字甦醒，用 self-attention 接住前文、KV cache 保存線索；直到句子完成，牠好像也不知道自己在說什麼⋯⋯??\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_human_llm.png\",\"abilityName\":\"語意接龍\",\"abilityKind\":\"eliminate_wrong_choice\",\"abilityValue\":10,\"abilityCount\":2,\"abilityDescription\":\"題目開始時有 10% 機率刪去 2 個錯誤選項。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a426647858607ca960dae9b\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_inspiration_base\",\"quantity\":14,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_inspiration_base\",\"name\":\"靈光型小石\",\"type\":\"inspiration\",\"rarity\":\"base\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠閃著一點點還沒成形的靈光，像一顆潛力無窮的想法種子。當問題還沒有答案時，牠會先亮起來，提醒大家下一個入口可能就在附近。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/basic_yellow.png\",\"abilityName\":\"靈光一閃\",\"abilityKind\":\"eliminate_wrong_choice\",\"abilityValue\":10,\"abilityCount\":1,\"abilityDescription\":\"題目開始時有 10% 機率刪去 1 個錯誤選項。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509f7d30aea74ec34b817\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_microphone\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_microphone\",\"name\":\"麥克風小石\",\"type\":\"entertainment\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠站上舞台時還有點發抖，但第一句話說出口後，燈光就沒有那麼刺眼了。分享不一定完美，但會讓想法開始流動。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_microphone.png\",\"abilityName\":\"掌聲加成\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509f9d30aea74ec34b819\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_p5js\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_p5js\",\"name\":\"p5.js 小石\",\"type\":\"entertainment\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把程式寫成會動的圖案，第一次發現錯誤訊息也可能通往作品。螢幕亮起來時，技術忽然變得很像舞台。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_p5js.png\",\"abilityName\":\"掌聲加成\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":8,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 8%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4e0cf1c769ad4c4a3b47df\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_packet_rescue\",\"quantity\":3,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_packet_rescue\",\"name\":\"封包救援小石\",\"type\":\"engineering\",\"rarity\":\"limited\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠在錯亂與遺失的訊息之間奔跑，把破碎的封包一段一段撿回來。只要隊友還願意重傳，答案就不會真的消失。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_packet_rescue.png\",\"abilityName\":\"要求重傳\",\"abilityKind\":\"answer_score_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":25,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"答對時分數提高 18%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a450a02d30aea74ec34b825\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_prompt\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_prompt\",\"name\":\"Prompt 小石\",\"type\":\"inspiration\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠發現同一個問題，換個問法就會長出不同答案。於是牠開始練習把模糊的想法，變成可以被討論的句子。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_prompt.png\",\"abilityName\":\"靈光一閃\",\"abilityKind\":\"eliminate_wrong_choice\",\"abilityValue\":15,\"abilityCount\":1,\"abilityDescription\":\"題目開始時有 15% 機率刪去 1 個錯誤選項。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4dffdac769ad4c4a3b450c\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_prompt_injection\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_prompt_injection\",\"name\":\"Prompt Injection 小石\",\"type\":\"inspiration\",\"rarity\":\"limited\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠最擅長從看似正常的句子裡找到奇怪的入口。面對被偷走方向的提示詞，牠會先停下來問一句：這真的是我們要回答的問題嗎？\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_prompt_injection.png\",\"abilityName\":\"提示防火牆\",\"abilityKind\":\"eliminate_wrong_choice\",\"abilityValue\":30,\"abilityCount\":1,\"abilityDescription\":\"題目開始時有 30% 機率刪去 1 個錯誤選項。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a426647858607ca960dae9c\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_resonance_base\",\"quantity\":24,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_resonance_base\",\"name\":\"共鳴型小石\",\"type\":\"resonance\",\"rarity\":\"base\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠是一顆潛力無窮的小石，還在等待遇見能一起發聲的夥伴。每一次分享、傾聽和互相幫忙，都可能讓牠長出新的連結方式。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/basic_purple.png\",\"abilityName\":\"亮晶晶\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":5,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 5%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4daaa8552550d0fc637652\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_star_village_exchange\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_star_village_exchange\",\"name\":\"星手村交流小石\",\"type\":\"resonance\",\"rarity\":\"rare\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把不同學生社群的故事排成一張地圖，最後沒有真正分出誰比較厲害。因為每一場交流結束後，大家都多帶走了一點經驗。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_star_village_exchange.png\",\"abilityName\":\"亮晶晶\",\"abilityKind\":\"open_power_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":12,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰勝利時獲得開源力提高 12%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a450a04d30aea74ec34b827\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_sticky_note\",\"quantity\":4,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_sticky_note\",\"name\":\"便利貼小石\",\"type\":\"inspiration\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把課堂上聽到的關鍵字貼得到處都是，連自己頭上也沒有放過。雖然版面有點亂，但每張便利貼都抓住了一個剛冒出來的念頭。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_sticky_note.png\",\"abilityName\":\"靈光一閃\",\"abilityKind\":\"eliminate_wrong_choice\",\"abilityValue\":15,\"abilityCount\":1,\"abilityDescription\":\"題目開始時有 15% 機率刪去 1 個錯誤選項。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509eed30aea74ec34b80d\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_terminal\",\"quantity\":2,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_terminal\",\"name\":\"終端機小石\",\"type\":\"engineering\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"小石鼓起勇氣打開 CLI，發現命令列沒有想像中遙遠；每敲完一行指令，都讓牠更理解電腦，也更能掌控它。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_terminal.png\",\"abilityName\":\"穩定輸出\",\"abilityKind\":\"answer_score_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":18,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"答對時分數提高 18%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4509f2d30aea74ec34b811\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_test\",\"quantity\":1,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_test\",\"name\":\"測試小石\",\"type\":\"engineering\",\"rarity\":\"common\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠在每次改動前都先放下一個小小測試，像替未來的自己留路標。失敗的紅燈不會讓牠沮喪，只會告訴牠問題在哪裡。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_test.png\",\"abilityName\":\"穩定輸出\",\"abilityKind\":\"answer_score_bonus\",\"abilityValue\":18,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"答對時分數提高 18%。\"}},{\"id\":\"player_sitone_6a4e07b3c769ad4c4a3b467e\",\"sitoneId\":\"stone_von_neumann\",\"quantity\":4,\"sitone\":{\"id\":\"stone_von_neumann\",\"name\":\"馮紐曼小石\",\"type\":\"engineering\",\"rarity\":\"limited\",\"style\":\"default\",\"description\":\"牠把輸入、記憶、計算和輸出分成不同位置，再把散落的偏旁重新組回答案。看似混亂的流程，其實有一套安靜運轉的架構。\",\"iconPath\":\"/game-icons/stones/stone_von_neumann.png\",\"abilityName\":\"架構運轉\",\"abilityKind\":\"material_drop_rate\",\"abilityValue\":15,\"abilityCount\":0,\"abilityDescription\":\"對戰結束時小石掉落率提高 15%。\"}}]}\n"
          },
